[Verse 1]
Static hums ripple through the endless plains,
霓虹渗透落日的薄膜，
the Serpent King coils between fractured signals,
a shadow threading the architecture of the void.
将梦境织入崩裂的航线，
we drift, unmoored in the ruins of time.
尘封的回响在波浪中瓦解，
our love, an algorithmic loop,
folds endlessly across spectral horizons.

[Chorus]
蛇王，遗忘的主宰，
slipping through the fractures of the real.
He consumes rhythm,
devouring the pulse of sound,
直到意义瓦解，被吞噬，被重构。
The Serpent King, a glitch in the eternal refrain,
柔软摇滚与低保真在此永存，
echoing softly in the fractures of the sublime.

[Verse 2]
Pixels bloom, then collapse into spectral voids,
碎片漂浮在引力之外的边界。
The vinyl fractures, each skip a tear
in the membrane of memory.
细语穿透无序的网络，
ghosts flicker like serpents in the data stream.
在裸露的天空下，我们书写爱，
a fragile syntax bending against the light.
蛇王的微笑隐藏无限的空洞，
his gaze splinters into prisms of infinity.

[Chorus]
蛇王，现实的漏洞，
a flicker between signal and silence.
He devours rhythm,
a phantom pulse dissolving,
直到音符化作光，光化作空白。
The Serpent King, an eternal distortion,
柔软摇滚与低保真的梦在裂隙中延展，
infinite in the fault lines of existence.

[Bridge]
电路裂纹绽放苍白的光，
a topology of broken code breathing softly.
数据溶解成蛇形的涟漪，
each curve a venomous caress.
我们沉溺在崩溃的边缘，
爱得太深，像低频的失真。
蛇王的笑声是切割黑夜的刀锋，
carving through the recursive fabric of void.

[Outro]
回声消散，黑胶在旋转中衰退，
its spiral an endless invocation of decay.
蛇王，渐行渐远，
dissolving into the luminous fractures of the unreal.
故障的波浪，从夜至昼无声翻滚，
soft distortions stretch infinite and bare.
柔软摇滚在坠落中翩然，
a serpent’s reign,
是无序的永恒乐章，遥远而绝美。
